<C>__{gandhi}
<D>__{sardar...}
<A>__{it means "leader" and it is the name the peasants have given patel. gandhi uses it with an intonation of novelty and respect. he stands and crosses to patel, clutching him emotionally, and it brings a bit of emotion from the sophisticated patel. gandhi holds him back to look at him.}
